    "It incorporates adaptive learning rates and momentum, which dynamically adjust the step sizes during optimization, making the training process more efficient Kingma & Ba (2014).",
    "All trainable parameters are initialized randomly using values sampled from a uniform distribution, following the approach of Glorot & Bengio (2010), and the value of regularization parameter λ is set to 10 -4.",
